{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_6_architectures", "label": "North-star 6 \u2014 Whole Mind / Is 2 Brains Enough?", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\6-architectures.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Two brains = a seed cell, not the organism (~4-6 roles); but you GROW into it \u2014 start with the smallest loop that thinks, let failure name the next module."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_6_architectures_hjepa", "label": "LeCun 'A Path' / H-JEPA", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\6-architectures.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "LeCun 2022: six modules (configurator/perception/world-model/cost/STM/actor) in one loop; JEPA = predict in latent, energy-based, anti-collapse (VICReg); maps heavily onto the substrate \u2014 missing piece is Actor Mode-2 planning."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_6_architectures_system12", "label": "System 1 / System 2", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\6-architectures.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Kahneman / Bengio & Goyal 2021: fast-parallel-reactive vs slow-serial-deliberate; Phase-1 built System 1 (SCFF+GD), Phase 2 builds System 2 on top \u2014 the cleanest one-line roadmap."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_6_architectures_thousand_brains", "label": "Thousand Brains Theory", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\6-architectures.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Hawkins/Numenta: ~150k cortical columns run the same algorithm on reference frames and VOTE; scale by replicate-t